  "description": "Adds a very strong mining utility",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fQH6bhQ.png\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"1000\" height=\"256\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rubble Ray mod is very inspired by an item from the classic minecraft mod OreSpawn, the Miner's Dream.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Rubble Ray item burns away the junk blocks leaving only ores exposed in a lengthy tunnel with light provided.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;The crafting recipe provides 3 rubble ray guns<br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q8E0FnO.png\" alt=\"recipe\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1377\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NRXbiUg.png\" alt=\"tunnel\" width=\"1125\" height=\"605\" /></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>I would like to thank TheyCallMeDanger for blessing this project. I did get into contact and TheyCallMeDanger is ok with this, im happy to provide proof</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
